text: "Proud of My Team" Jack Smith Defends Jan. 6 & Docs Cases | DRM News | AC1FSpecial Counsel Jack Smith delivers powerful, unflinching testimony before House Judiciary Committee: "I stand by every decision – Trump criminally schemed to overturn 2020 election." Smith defends charges as fact- and law-based, slams revenge attacks on prosecutors, warns rule of law is fragile, and reaffirms: "No one is above the law." Historic defense amid Trump pressure. For more details, watch our story and subscribe to our channel, DRM News.
